casebody.data:
TIMBERLAKE, Respondent, v. PRATT, Appellant. (City Court of New York,

General Term.

April 28, 1897.) Action by Channing S. Timberlake against Charles M. Pratt. John Aitkén, for appellant. Menken Bros., for respondent. PER CURIAM.

This is an appeal from an order denying judgment debtor’s motion to vacate order in supplementary proceedings. Order affirmed, with costs.
